items.name: Witch's Hat
trivia: * The Witch's Hat is one of the only items above the standard dimensions for an accessory. According to rumours, this is because the staff were still deciding on whether high definition items have a place in Moonbounce at the time of creating it.

items.name: Puff
trivia: * Puff was sourced from [https://grafxkid.itch.io/sprite-pack-4 GrafxKid's Sprite Pack 4].
* Puff is the first event exclusive item in Moonbounce. It was available during the Halloween event in 2023.
* Puff is the favorite character of the user and Wiki team member [[User:Bane|Bane]].

items.name: Fortune
trivia: * The number sequence on the fortune (1, 6, 7, 13), is a [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Constant-recursive_sequence constant-recursive sequence]. Adding two numbers together gives the next number in the sequence. A more popular example of this is the Fibonacci sequence.
